The paper proposes a hybrid hardware-software framework for on-device machine learning, specifically for image classification. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of deep networks, which could place it in the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the potential for increased autonomy, which could suggest a connection to the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category.
